    "steps": [
        {
            "stepNo": 1,
            "content": "預熱焗爐至攝氏100度。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/6e9634bc-9b03-4a4d-ba1a-17ab14fdb8f4",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 2,
            "content": "準備一個碗，加入海鹽、黑胡椒、芫茜籽粉、甜椒粉、紅椒粉、黃芥末粉及胡椒粉拌勻備用。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/fd008eda-14bc-4355-9b49-f36f5a53a7af",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 3,
            "content": "準備另一個碗，加入橄欖油及蒜蓉拌勻備用。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/1209e920-7237-41a2-832e-472410458654",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 4,
            "content": "將牛柳吸乾血水，表面塗上蒜蓉橄欖油，將混合香料均勻沾上牛柳表面。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/88fc88a4-27fe-4261-9295-2ad02c67cd8c",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 5,
            "content": "準備4張錫紙(可以完整包起牛柳的大小即可)，用錫紙重複包裹牛柳4次，放入焗盤焗4小時，取出待涼，放入雪櫃冷藏至少半天備用。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/9ccb8573-2c62-413a-946a-2a3f0114d124",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 6,
            "content": "將紫椰菜及椰菜切絲；準備一個碗，加入所有蔬菜拌勻；準備湯鍋，加入所有調味加熱煮滾成醬汁。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/71f57f07-1162-4c27-957d-5b13c23b4cbc",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 7,
            "content": "將煮好的醬汁，分數次加入蔬菜碗輕輕拌勻，降溫後放入密封罐，冷藏保存。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/d2d5b4de-9897-4d65-9d51-e5eb3d988084",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 8,
            "content": "預熱焗爐至攝氏200度。將鹹牛肉的錫紙拿走，鹹牛肉放入焗爐焗7分鐘，直到表面金黃色，切薄片備用。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/8017089b-4444-4788-8577-5045c89f15a4",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 9,
            "content": "9.取一平底锅，加热切片面包至上色即可，面包表面抹上芥末酱，放上牛肉片，再放上面包片，用牙签固定对切，搭配卷心菜沙拉和酸黄瓜，享用即成。",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20161014/891ca28c-2407-4ded-8594-b737743d39ee",
            "languageId": null
        }
    ],
